      </m:math>.  Using induction, we conclude that the previous
      condition will be necessary and sufficient for orthonormality
      of
      <m:math>
	<m:set>
	  <m:bvar>
	    <m:apply>
	      <m:ci type="fn"><m:msub>
		  <m:mi>φ</m:mi>
